| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1560 — Recovery Inhibition (cicada3301)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3cbe51c5-1e30-5fa6-8300-62d2dc3efdb8"
